column2: SELECT #  p.cModelMag_g,  p.cModelMag_r,   p.cModelMag_i,   p.cModelMag_z,   p.cModelMagErr_g,   p.cModelMagErr_r,   p.cModelMagErr_i,   p.cModelMagErr_z,   p.objID,  p.ra,   p.dec,   s.z,   s.zErr,   s.ra,   s.dec,  pz.z,  pz.zErr from Galaxy as p LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll as s ON p.objID = s.objID  LEFT JOIN photoz as pz ON p.objID = pz.objID  WHERE pz.z <= #
